# Documentation backpressure

A task is **not complete** until living docs under `docs/` match the change. Templates are copy-only.

**Templates:** `docs/context/TEMPLATE.md`, `docs/adr/template.md`, `docs/specs/TEMPLATE.md`

**Index:** [docs/README.md](../docs/README.md). Root keeps only `README.md` + `.cursor/rules/`.

## After every code or behavior change

| Change type | Update |
|-------------|--------|
| Edits under `app/` | [docs/context/app.md](../docs/context/app.md) |
| Edits under `assets/` (brand kit or app media) | [docs/context/assets.md](../docs/context/assets.md) |
| Edits under `components/` | `docs/context/components.md` (create from template if missing) |
| Edits under `hooks/` or `constants/` | `docs/context/<scope>.md` if that scope file exists |
| New domain term or role | [docs/context/project.md](../docs/context/project.md) → Ontology |
| Local design choice | relevant `docs/context/*.md` → Decisions |
| Code pattern change | relevant `docs/context/*.md` → Patterns |
| New hard rule | relevant `docs/context/*.md` → Policies |
| Shipped feature with spec | matching `docs/specs/*.md` — check ACs |
| Architecture decision | `docs/adr/ADR-NNN-*.md` + [overview.md](../docs/adr/overview.md) |
| Completed planned work | [implementation-plan.md](../docs/implementation-plan.md) |
| End of session | [progress.md](../docs/progress.md) |
| User-visible capability changed | [current.md](../docs/current.md) |
| Brand, UI tokens, or copy tone | [brand.md](../docs/brand.md) |
| Org account access (no secrets in repo) | [accounts-and-access.md](../docs/accounts-and-access.md) |
| Agent commands or repo layout | [agents.md](../docs/agents.md) |
| Product vision or setup | root `README.md` only |

## Verification before “done”

```bash
npx tsc --noEmit
npm run lint    # when relevant
npm test        # when relevant
```

## When unsure

- Spec exists? Check off ACs in `docs/specs/` before claiming done.
- Architectural? ADR + link from [project.md](../docs/context/project.md).
- What runs today changed? Update [current.md](../docs/current.md).
